# TaxBackwards.ca — Master Project Reference
> Single source of truth for Claude and Cursor. Read this at the start of every session.
> Last updated: May 25, 2026

---

## 1. Project Overview

TaxBackwards.ca is a Canadian reverse sales tax calculator for bookkeepers, freelancers, sole proprietors, and small business owners. Users enter a gross transaction total, select a province, and receive:
- A net consideration base (pre-tax amount)
- A claimable Input Tax Credit (ITC) amount

**All calculations run entirely client-side. No backend. No API calls. No external dependencies.**

**Domain:** taxbackwards.ca  
**Hosting:** Cloudflare Pages (connected to GitHub repo, auto-deploys on push to `main`)  
**License:** GPL-3.0 (forces copycats to open-source their entire project)  
**Analytics:** Cloudflare Web Analytics or Plausible (cookieless — no consent banner needed)  
**Operational cost:** ~$12/year CAD (domain only)

