## 7. UI Terminology — Enforced Everywhere

| Context | Correct Label | Never Use |
|---|---|---|
| Input field | `Total Paid (Gross Transaction Amount)` | "Price", "Receipt Total" |
| Net output | `Base Cost (Net Consideration)` | "Pre-Tax Price" |
| Tax output | `Tax Removed (Input Tax Credit / ITC Eligible)` | "Tax Back", "Refund" |
| Province selector | `Target Jurisdiction` | just "Province" |
| Auditor toggle | `Activate Auditor Precision View Mode (4 Decimals)` | — |
| **Never use the word "refund" anywhere in the UI** | | |

