## 12. CSS & Print Rules

- Print media queries **must** be in `src/css/style.css` — never a separate file (CSP conflict)
- `@media print` must hide: `header, footer, aside, button, .help-icon, select, input, .cookie-banner`
- `@media print` must show: `.print-only-ledger-header`
- Print font: system sans-serif stack — **never Courier New**
- Print page: `letter portrait`, margins `0.6in 0.8in`
- All print text forced to `#000000` on `#ffffff`
- Print logo: swap `logo.svg` → `logo-print.svg` via `@media print`

