## 13. SEO & Schema Rules

- Every HTML page must include a `FinancialProduct` JSON-LD schema in `<head>`
- `index.html` must also include a `FAQPage` JSON-LD schema
- Every page must have a `<link rel="canonical">` tag
- `<html>` must have `lang="en-CA"` on English pages, `lang="fr-CA"` on Quebec sub-pages
- Meta description must be present and unique on every page
- Footer links to public GitHub repo for E-E-A-T authority

