## 18. Monetization Strategy

### Phase 1 (MVP launch) — No ads
- Affiliate marketing only
- Wave Accounting affiliate (Impact.com) — apply 1–3 weeks post-launch
- FreshBooks (ShareASale) — apply 30 days after Wave
- QuickBooks Canada (CJ Affiliate) — apply after 3 months traffic
- Affiliate link placement: text link below ITC output results panel — never a banner

### Phase 2 (Month 3–6, after provincial sub-pages exist)
- Apply to Google AdSense only after sufficient content volume exists
- Use manually placed static ad units in fixed positions — **never Auto Ads**
- If AdSense added: geofence CMP consent banner to Quebec visitors only via Cloudflare Workers
- Gate only AdSense behind consent — not the calculator itself

### Phase 3 (Month 6–12, traffic >10K/month)
- Evaluate Ezoic or Mediavine header bidding

**Realistic first revenue: 8–14 weeks post-launch (affiliate)**  
**Realistic SEO traction: 12–24 months to meaningful organic traffic**

