## 19. Privacy & Legal

- Plausible Analytics: cookieless — no consent banner required
- Quebec Law 25: triggered the moment AdSense loads behavioral cookies — requires opt-in CMP
- PIPEDA compliance language on privacy page covers all Canadian users
- Never mix user financial input data with any analytics payload
- IP anonymization if Google Analytics ever used

