## 21. Maintenance Calendar

### Monthly (~30 min)
- Check affiliate dashboards for commissions and link integrity
- Review analytics for traffic trends and anomalies
- Verify Cloudflare dashboard shows no security alerts

### Quarterly (~2–3 hrs)
- Run `npm audit` and apply fixes
- Run `npx playwright test` — verify all outbound links return 200
- Manually verify key provincial tax rates against canada.ca
- Update `LAST_VERIFIED` in `taxRates.js`
- Rotate Discord webhook if applicable
- Check Cloudflare security settings

### Annually (~4–6 hrs)
- Full review of all provincial sub-page content
- Review FAQPage JSON-LD schema for accuracy
- Domain renewal at Hover (set 30-day reminder)
- Review affiliate relationships
- Review CSP headers for any new third-party scripts
- Full cross-browser and cross-device testing pass

### As-Needed (event-triggered)
| Trigger | Action | Time |
|---|---|---|
| Federal/provincial budget announces tax change | Update `taxRates.js`, run tests, push | 15–30 min |
| CRA website breaks a link | Find new URL, update, run tests | 10–15 min |
| Google Search Console flags structured data error | Fix JSON-LD schema | 20–30 min |
| npm audit reports high severity | Apply fix, run tests, deploy | 15–30 min |

**Rate change early warning system:** Free Google Alert for `"GST HST rate change"` — covers both federal and provincial levels.

